fulltitle: Two views on the crash of Flight 553 w/ Sherman Skolnik (1973)
title: Two views on the crash of Flight 553 w/ Sherman Skolnik (1973)
_filename: _Two views on the crash of Flight 553 w_ Sherman Skolnik (1973).mp4
description:
ORIGINAL: https://calisphere.org/item/c328dcff2fe270175dbe624d6720c2b9/
Two radio presentations about the crash of Flight 553, which killed Dorothy Hunt, the wife of #Watergate conspirator E. Howard Hunt.
'The Mysterious Death of Mrs. E. Howard Hunt', an interview with Sherman Skolnik
'The Midway Plane Crash: Was it a Conspiracy?', radio documentary critiquing the conspiracy case of Sheman Skolnik

For more related content, please visit: 
http://ourhiddenhistory.org/
https://archive.org/details/@altviewstv-fanclub
